---
import Layout from "../../layouts/Layout.astro";
import ShapeFooter from "../../components/ShapeFooter.astro";
---

<Layout
  title="Tim doi tac NocoBase - Mang dich vu toan cau cho du an cua ban"
  description="NocoBase co mang doi tac toan cau cung cap phat trien he thong, tich hop, trien khai va bao tri. Hay cho chung toi biet nhu cau cua ban va chung toi se giup ket noi dung doi tac."
  keywords="NocoBase partner, tim doi tac, phat trien he thong, tich hop he thong, ho tro ky thuat, trien khai"
>
  <section class="bg-half-170 bg-light d-table w-100">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="row justify-content-center">
        <div class="col-lg-8 col-md-10 text-center">
          <div class="title-heading">
            <span class="badge bg-soft-primary mb-3">Tim doi tac</span>
            <h1 class="fw-bold mt-2 mb-3">Tim doi tac NocoBase phu hop de day nhanh du an cua ban</h1>
            <p class="para-desc mx-auto text-muted">NocoBase co mang doi tac toan cau cung cap phat trien, tich hop, trien khai va bao tri tren NocoBase de giup du an cua ban tien ve phia truoc mot cach chac chan hon.</p>
            <div class="mt-4 pt-2">
              <a href="#submit-requirements" class="btn btn-primary me-3"><i class="uil uil-file-edit-alt me-1"></i>Gui nhu cau</a>
              <a href="#partner-fit" class="btn btn-outline-primary"><i class="uil uil-arrow-down me-1"></i>Xem them</a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section" id="partner-fit">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="row justify-content-center"><div class="col-12"><div class="section-title text-center mb-4 pb-2"><h4 class="title mb-3">Khi nao nen lam viec voi doi tac</h4><p class="para-desc mx-auto text-muted mb-0">Neu ban dang o mot trong cac tinh huong duoi day, doi tac NocoBase co the giup du an van hanh hieu qua hon.</p></div></div></div>
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-6 mt-4 pt-2"><div class="card border-0 features feature-primary feature-clean course-feature p-4 overflow-hidden shadow h-100"><div class="icons text-start"><i class="uil uil-users-alt rounded h3 mb-0"></i></div><div class="card-body p-0 mt-4 d-flex flex-column"><h5 class="title text-dark mb-2">Doi ngu noi bo cua ban chua du nang luc</h5><p class="text-muted">Neu doi ngu cua ban thieu thoi gian hoac kinh nghiem trien khai, doi tac co the nhanh chong bo sung va giu du an di dung huong.</p><i class="uil uil-users-alt full-img"></i></div></div></div>
        <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-6 mt-4 pt-2"><div class="card border-0 features feature-primary feature-clean course-feature p-4 overflow-hidden shadow h-100"><div class="icons text-start"><i class="uil uil-rocket rounded h3 mb-0"></i></div><div class="card-body p-0 mt-4 d-flex flex-column"><h5 class="title text-dark mb-2">Ban can trien khai he thong kinh doanh nhanh</h5><p class="text-muted">Khi toc do la yeu to quan trong, dich vu doi tac co the rut ngan duong di tu ke hoach den van hanh, dong thoi giam rui ro trien khai.</p><i class="uil uil-rocket full-img"></i></div></div></div>
        <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-6 mt-4 pt-2"><div class="card border-0 features feature-primary feature-clean course-feature p-4 overflow-hidden shadow h-100"><div class="icons text-start"><i class="uil uil-setting rounded h3 mb-0"></i></div><div class="card-body p-0 mt-4 d-flex flex-column"><h5 class="title text-dark mb-2">Ban can phat trien theo yeu cau, dao tao hoac bao tri</h5><p class="text-muted">Neu ban can nhieu hon mot phan mem va muon co su dong hanh lau dai, hop tac voi doi tac thuong la lua chon dang tin cay hon.</p><i class="uil uil-setting full-img"></i></div></div></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="row justify-content-center"><div class="col-12"><div class="section-title text-center mb-4 pb-2"><h4 class="title mb-4">Doi tac NocoBase co the ho tro ban nhu the nao</h4><p class="para-desc mx-auto text-muted mb-0">Du la xay dung he thong moi hay nang cap he thong hien co, cac doi tac NocoBase deu cung cap dich vu chuyen nghiep tu dau den cuoi.</p></div></div></div>
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-6 mt-4 pt-2"><div class="card border-0 features feature-primary feature-clean course-feature p-4 overflow-hidden shadow h-100"><div class="icons text-start"><i class="uil uil-laptop-cloud rounded h3 mb-0"></i></div><div class="card-body p-0 mt-4"><h5 class="title text-dark">Phat trien he thong</h5><p class="text-muted mt-2">Xay dung ung dung duoc tuy chinh theo nhu cau kinh doanh, tu phan tich yeu cau va thiet ke giai phap den phat trien va ban giao.</p><i class="uil uil-laptop-cloud full-img"></i></div></div></div>
        <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-6 mt-4 pt-2"><div class="card border-0 features feature-primary feature-clean course-feature p-4 overflow-hidden shadow h-100"><div class="icons text-start"><i class="uil uil-link-alt rounded h3 mb-0"></i></div><div class="card-body p-0 mt-4"><h5 class="title text-dark">Tich hop he thong</h5><p class="text-muted mt-2">Ket noi NocoBase voi ERP, CRM, OA va cac nen tang hien co de xoa bo silo du lieu va dong bo hoa quy trinh kinh doanh.</p><i class="uil uil-link-alt full-img"></i></div></div></div>
        <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-6 mt-4 pt-2"><div class="card border-0 features feature-primary feature-clean course-feature p-4 overflow-hidden shadow h-100"><div class="icons text-start"><i class="uil uil-setting rounded h3 mb-0"></i></div><div class="card-body p-0 mt-4"><h5 class="title text-dark">Ho tro ky thuat</h5><p class="text-muted mt-2">Trien khai, bao tri phien ban, toi uu hieu nang va xu ly su co de he thong NocoBase cua ban hoat dong on dinh va hieu qua.</p><i class="uil uil-setting full-img"></i></div></div></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section" id="submit-requirements">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="row justify-content-center"><div class="col-12 text-center"><h4 class="title mb-4">Gui nhu cau cua ban</h4><p class="text-muted para-desc mx-auto mb-4">Hay cho chung toi biet yeu cau du an, va chung toi se ket noi ban voi doi tac NocoBase phu hop nhat.</p></div></div>
      <div class="row justify-content-center"><div class="col-lg-8 col-md-10"><div class="card border-0 shadow rounded overflow-hidden"><iframe src="https://service-en.nocobase.com/public-forms/lf5m0yjz5dq" style="width: 100%; min-height: 700px; border: none;" loading="lazy"></iframe></div></div></div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <ShapeFooter />
</Layout>
